10// FastEmit Immediate Predicate functions.
11static bool Predicate_imm32SExt16(int64_t Imm) {
12
13 // imm32SExt16 predicate - True if the i32 immediate fits in a 16-bit
14 // sign extended field. Used by instructions like 'addi'.
15 return (int32_t)Imm == (short)Imm;
16
17}
18static bool Predicate_imm64SExt16(int64_t Imm) {
19
20 // imm64SExt16 predicate - True if the i64 immediate fits in a 16-bit
21 // sign extended field. Used by instructions like 'addi'.
22 return (int64_t)Imm == (short)Imm;
23
24}
25static bool Predicate_immSExt5NonZero(int64_t Imm) {
26 return Imm && isInt<5>(Imm);
27}
28static bool Predicate_i32immNonAllOneNonZero(int64_t Imm) {
29 return Imm && (Imm != -1);
30}

4877// Top-level FastEmit function.
4878
4879unsigned fastEmit_ri(MVT VT, MVT RetVT, unsigned Opcode, unsigned Op0, bool Op0IsKill, uint64_t imm1) override {
4880 if (VT == MVT::i32 && Predicate_imm32SExt16(imm1))
4881 if (unsigned Reg = fastEmit_ri_Predicate_imm32SExt16(VT, RetVT, Opcode, Op0, Op0IsKill, imm1))
4882 return Reg;
4883
4884 if (VT == MVT::i64 && Predicate_imm64SExt16(imm1))
4885 if (unsigned Reg = fastEmit_ri_Predicate_imm64SExt16(VT, RetVT, Opcode, Op0, Op0IsKill, imm1))
4886 return Reg;
4887
4888 switch (Opcode) {
4889 case ISD::SRA: return fastEmit_ISD_SRA_ri(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, imm1);
4890 case PPCISD::EXTSWSLI: return fastEmit_PPCISD_EXTSWSLI_ri(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, imm1);
4891 case PPCISD::TC_RETURN: return fastEmit_PPCISD_TC_RETURN_ri(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, imm1);
4892 default: return 0;
4893 }
4894}
